******************
**Challenge 2970**
******************
    This challenge requires creation of new servers

To create a new server, go to the server list page and click on the Create Server
button next to the Search filter.

*****************
**Files Changed**
*****************
public/js/app.js
    New route to create server added

public/js/services.js
    New action to create server added

public/js/controllers.js
    New controller for the creation of server added.
    Also, new function to change the location to creation of server from listing the server added

public/views/pages/server-create.html
    New template for creation of server added

public/views/pages/servers.html
    Code to direct user to creation of server from server list page added

